---
title: Mumbai Beef Schnitzel with Bombay Potatoes & Radish Salad
description: Secure that apron because you'll be crumbing up some spiced beef schnitzels and roasting Bombay potatoes to golden perfection for dinner
tonight. Paired with a crisp radish salad, you're going to be surprised by the fun and fanciful flavour combinations that are sure to please.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
